translations: [动] 食虫的，以虫类为食的；食虫动植物的

sentences.sentence: Rex was a large carnivore; insectivorous plants are considered carnivores.
sentences.translation: 暴龙是一种大型的食肉动物；食虫植物被看作食肉动物。

sentences.sentence: Two insectivorous mites were released to tea fields to control injurious mites.
sentences.translation: 在茶园释放两种食虫性螨，用以控制茶叶害螨。

sentences.sentence: Tyrannosaurus Rex was a large carnivore; insectivorous plants are considered carnivores.
